				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6bd38df1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="6bd38df1" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p><strong data-start="442" data-end="479">It all starts with a conversation</strong><br data-start="479" data-end="482" />Simply share your target capacity, battery specifications, and project scope.<br data-start="559" data-end="562" />Our team will develop an initial plan and roadmap for your lithium battery project within 24 hours.<br data-start="661" data-end="664" />Taking the first step towards your custom solution is that easy.</p>								</div>
