		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3c856419 elementor-hidden-tablet elementor-hidden-mobile e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="3c856419" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}">
					<div class="e-con-inner">
		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-424fb24 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="424fb24" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f55b6d4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="f55b6d4" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Our Core Services</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-79265ef elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="79265ef" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									In the competitive battery landscape, clarity is power. We offer two core services to provide that clarity. <br>From independent battery validation to hands-on manufacturing training, we equip your team with the data and skills essential for success. <br>Let us help you build a stronger, more competitive business.								</div>
				</div>
				</div>
		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b942f8c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="b942f8c" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
