		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-7d4c426b e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="7d4c426b" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-4edc0eb0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="4edc0eb0" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h6 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Xiaowei Lithium Battery Profile</h6>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3fa2d49e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="3fa2d49e" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h6 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Specialize in battery equipment manufacturing for more than 20+ years.</h6>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-479bd1e6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="479bd1e6" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ae1c155 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="ae1c155" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p>Guangdong Xiaowei New Energy Technology Co., Ltd. is a turnkey provider and manufacturer of battery equipment. We deliver end-to-end servicesâprocess design, equipment manufacturing, installation, commissioning, and after-salesâto accelerate ramp-up and improve yield for R&amp;D lines and gigafactories.</p><p>Complete equipment for coin, cylindrical, pouch, and prismatic cells. From mixing, coating, calendaring, slitting, stacking/winding, electrolyte filling, sealing, formation, grading, to testing and packaging. Reduce unit manufacturing cost while meeting safety and quality standards across lab, pilot, and mass production stages.</p></div></div>								</div>
				</div>
		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f8a1b77 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="f8a1b77" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-60ef8a94 elementor-align-left elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="60ef8a94" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<div class="elementor-button-wrapper">
					<a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="/xiaowei-company">
						<span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper">
									<span class="elementor-button-text">Explore Our Story</span>
					</span>
					</a>
				</div>
								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9f95aa0 elementor-align-left elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="9f95aa0" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<div class="elementor-button-wrapper">
					<a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="https://xiaoweitop.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Catalogue-Company-Profile-Xiaowei-New-Energy.pdf?x48432" target="_blank">
